query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(it1 mi) NoHashJoin(it1 mi at) NoMergeJoin(at cn ct it1 mc mi t mk) NoHashJoin(at cn ct it1 mc mi mk t k) */ select min(mi.info) AS release_date,
min(t.title) AS internet_movie
from info_type AS it1
inner join movie_info AS mi
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'release dates' AND mi.note like '%internet%' AND mi.info like 'USA:% 200%'
inner join aka_title AS at
on mi.movie_id = at.movie_id
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = at.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = at.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.note like '%(200%)%' AND mc.note like '%(worldwide)%'
inner join company_type AS ct
on ct.id = mc.company_type_id
inner join company_name AS cn
on cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = at.movie_id
inner join keyword AS k
on k.id = mk.keyword_id;
